snippet.title: Baby News! Rich Homie Quan's Girlfriend Amber Shows Off Her Massive Baby Bump & Reveal Baby Gender!
snippet.description:
Dequantes Devontay Lamar, better known by his stage name Rich Homie Quan, is an American rapper, singer and songwriter. He was previously signed to independent label T.I.G. Entertainment and is currently with Motown Records.
